== Vavr, jivit ==
Borkar adim [[Akaxvanni]], Ponnjecho Station Director aslo. Ek vitravpi koso, tannem sorkaran choloilolea reddio stexon aslolea [[Mumboi]], [[Mungllur]] ani [[Kolhapur]] vavurla.

2015 vorsa, Borkaran [[Pundalik Narayan Naik]] hacho zago [[Goa Konkani Akademi]][2] cho Iezman mhonn ghetlo.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Veteran-Konkani-poet-Madhav-Borkar-took-charge-of-office-as-the-president-of-Goa-Konkani-Akademi-in-Panaji-on-Monday-/articleshow/47591872.cms|title=Veteran Konkani poet Madhav Borkar took charge of office as the president of Goa Konkani Akademi in Panaji on Monday.&nbsp; - Times of India|work=The Times of India|access-date=2018-06-21}}</ref> Mars 2018 vorsa, tannem kovitent 50 vorsam purnn kelim ani tannem atth kovnache khondd uzvaddaileat.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.goa365.tv/balcao/balcao-madhav-borkar-celebrates-50-years-of-his-poetry/program/00083.html|title=GOA365 VIDEO: Balcao - Madhav Borkar Celebrates 50 Years of his Poetry|work=Goa365|access-date=2018-06-21|language=en}}</ref> Tannem Mankarnika kodden logn zoddlam ani tankam don bhurgim asat, dhuv Yogini ani put Chinmay.<ref name="Sahitya">{{Cite web|url=http://sahitya-akademi.gov.in/sahitya-akademi/library/meettheauthor/madhav_borcar.pdf|title=Meet the Author: Madhav Borcar|last=|first=|date=|website=Sahitya Akademi|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=July 3, 2018}}</ref>

== Sahitik borovp ==

Borkar kovita 1968 vorsa savn borovnk laglo. Tachi poili punji to xallent aslo ten’na uzvaddavpant aili. 15 vorsanche piraier tachi ''Chanvar''  chhap’pant aili. Tache kodden so kovitancheo punji ani don bhaxantoram asat. -- Kabir zacho borovpi Prabhakar Machve ani ''Ekxem Ek Kovita'' borovpi  Rabindranath Tagore.<ref name="Sahitya" />  Tachea kovitechea vavrant ''Chonvar'' (The Bloom, 1969), ''Votacheo Savlleo'' (The Shadows of Sunlight, 1972), ''Uzvaddacho Rukh'' (The Tree of Light, 1975), ''Porzollachem Dar ''(The Door to Brightness, 1986), ''Yaman'' (Yaman, 1999), ''Avyaktachim Gannim'' (Songs of the Unexpressed, 2002), ani ''Symphony'' (Symphony, 2012).</span>''. ''Tache kodden ek punji asa zaka  ''Mollbachem Zonel ''mhonn vollkhopant ieta.

== Tosripam, adi ==
Survatechea tachea borovpache karkidint, taka Bharotio  Sahiteo Akademi  tosrip 2001 vorsa, tachea Yaman, kovitechea punjek favo zalam.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/goa/Madhav-Borkar-appointed-GKA-president/articleshow/47548582.cms|title=Madhav Borkar appointed GKA president - Times of India|work=The Times of India|access-date=2018-06-21}}</ref>

